---

## ğŸ” Security

- **No hardcoded secrets**: Use `.env.local` (gitignored) and GitHub Encrypted Secrets
- **Input validation**: Zod schemas on all API routes
- **Rate limiting**: Upstash Redis (5 req/hour per IP)
- **Spam protection**: Cloudflare Turnstile
- **Dependency audits**: Dependabot + `pnpm audit`
- **Code scanning**: CodeQL + ESLint security plugin
- **HTTPS only**: Enforced via Vercel/Azure

### Required GitHub Secrets

```
VERCEL_TOKEN          # Vercel deployment token
VERCEL_ORG_ID         # Your Vercel org ID
VERCEL_PROJECT_ID     # Your Vercel project ID
SMTP_HOST             # Email SMTP host
SMTP_USER             # Email username
SMTP_PASS             # Email password
TURNSTILE_SECRET_KEY  # Cloudflare Turnstile secret
```

---

## ğŸ§ª Testing

- **Unit Tests**: Components, utilities (Vitest + Testing Library)
- **E2E Tests**: User flows (Playwright)
- **Coverage Goal**: 80%+ (enforced in CI)

```bash
pnpm test:coverage    # Generate coverage report
pnpm test:e2e         # Run Playwright tests
```

---

## ğŸš€ Deployment

### Vercel (Recommended)

```bash
# Install Vercel CLI
npm install -g vercel

# Deploy preview
vercel

# Deploy production (requires GitHub approval)
git push origin main
```

### Manual Deployment

```bash
pnpm build
pnpm start
```

### Docker

```bash
docker build -t qwe-app .
docker run -p 3000:3000 --env-file .env.local qwe-app
```

