## ğŸ“Š Analytics

**Plausible Analytics** (privacy-focused, GDPR-compliant)

- No cookies
- No personal data collection
- Simple, auditable metrics

Add to `.env.local`:
```
NEXT_PUBLIC_PLAUSIBLE_DOMAIN=yourfirm.com
```

